com.clearblade.platform.api.internal

Class RequestProperties

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.clearblade.platform.api.internal.RequestProperties

  • public class RequestProperties
extends java.lang.Object
    This class consists of instance methods that create and modify http headers that will be used in calls to the API.

    Headers are typically used in conjunction with the Request Engine Class like so: 

     RequestProperties headers = new RequestProperties.Builder(ClearBlade.getUri(), ClearBlade.getCallTimeOut()).build();
 request.setHeaders(headers);

    Since:
    1.0
    Author:
    CBIII
    See Also:
    RequestEngine
